                        <interp inst="t18661217-142-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been convicted of a like offence in April</hi>, 1865, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps"> PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.**†—<hi rend="italic">
